/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=39da474c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國聯署 deadline 3/1 仲要7000人 <br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=ba9fbf00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\ndeadline fighters 請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4404b7e6d443bb1dfd33ed3c5c0579488774b4dc","tid":1803960,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea9d57fef4e5fda06ba2c275169596860c7de34","tid":1803960,"uid":89542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"其實我都想講，無人唔支持獨立<br />\n但正如樓主所講獨立如果無治權根本無用<br />\n所以無論如何獨立路線圖只剩下<br />\n支爆，支解，獨立，真普選<br />\n所以今時今日係度寫post改口號，唔做實事既<br />\n唔係豬隊友就係分化5毛<br />\n改口號會引起大量不必要分化，又影響國際戰線<br />\n又睇唔到有咩好處<br />\n如果唔係5毛，果個真係豬到爆既隊友"},{"pid":"d8532edfa917617f1a42c8b6fdd4c8c28f5bfd04","tid":1803960,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"同意。推<br />\n想嗌就嗌，反正你上到街佢點都扣咗你帽子(老屈)先"}]}